data.description: Situated on top of a hill, this stunning 4 bed,2 1/2 bath home has been thoughtfully updated to cater to your every need,making it an ideal sanctuary for anyone looking to create their forever home. Step inside to a welcoming foyer that leads to a freshly redone kitchen,ready to inspire culinary adventures. Equipped with stainless steel appliances, ample storage,including a back kitchen to meal prep and hide appliances,this kitchen was designed for both style and functionality. Designated laundry room adds to your convenience,ensuring smooth home management. The heart of this home is its inviting living areas,freshly painted and waiting for you to add your personal touch. Gather around the cozy living room fireplace or step outside to the back entertainment area featuring fire pit and pergola setting the stage for unforgettable outdoor gatherings overlooking the 15th hole. 3 acres of land stun in springtime when everything blooms. There's nothing left to do but make an offer!
